V/S: BP 142/88, HR 92, RR 16, Temp 37.6°C
PE: 1st MTP joint ซ้าย: erythema, swelling, exquisite tenderness, ROM ลด

Lab: WBC 11,800, ESR 56, CRP 24, Uric acid 8.6, Cr 1.0
